CN: 居然敢炸我的车，我看你是想吃枪子儿了
EN: How dare you blow up my car? I think you want to get shot!

CN: 江湖人称疯狂加特林就是我，去死吧！
EN: I'm what they call crazy Gatling.  Go to hell!

CN: 这个枪子儿就是为你准备的，小的们上！
EN: This bullet is prepared for you.

CN: 放心，这只是帮派之间的“友好”交流！
EN: Don't worry, this is just "friendly" communication between gangs!

CN: 把你打成马蜂窝就是几秒钟的事儿！
EN: It's too easy to kill you!

CN: 让你感受感受恐怖的滋味，别吓得尿裤子！
EN: Let you feel the taste of horror. Don't be so scared that you want to run away

CN: 多么美丽的雾气，剧毒又致命！
EN: What a beautiful mist, but it's deadly and poisonous!

CN: 我就是剧毒的化身，痛苦的死去吧！
EN: I am the incarnation of poison, so you can only die in pain!

CN: 想和我较量？你还不够资格
EN: Do you want to compete with me? You are not level enough to compete with me.

CN: 带着遗憾温柔的去死吧！
EN: Die a gentle death with regret

CN: 美丽的闪电会把你劈成两半！
EN: Beautiful lightning will split you in half!

CN: 看见这滋滋滋的电流了吗，你马上就能体会到这美妙的滋味！
EN: Do you hear the electricity? You can feel the wonderful taste right away!

CN: 居然敢惹我，我可是帮派里面物理学的最好的！
EN: How dare you offend me? I'm the best physicist in the gang!

CN: 我看你真的是吃了豹子胆了，看我不把你电个鸡飞狗跳！
EN: I think you are supercilious, so I must punish you now

CN: 闪电！闪电！闪电！召唤闪电！哈哈哈哈哈！
EN: Lightning! Lightning! Lightning! Summon lightning! Ha ha ha ha ha ha ha!

CN: 遇上了我，让你酥酥麻麻的去死！
EN: When you met me, you can only be electrocuted to death.

CN: 这街区的治安越来越差了，连警察都敢打！
EN: The law and order in this neighborhood is getting worse and worse, and now people even dare to fight the police!

CN: 小小帮派也敢和我叫嚣，看我一手捏死你！
EN: The small-scale gang dare to provoke me and now see me how easily I kill you.

CN: 看来是时候肃清一下这个街道上的纪律了
EN: It seems it's time to manage the discipline on this street.

CN: 我要亲自动手把你们全部送进监狱里去！
EN: I will personally send all of you to prison!

CN: 居然连警车都敢共攻击，看我怎么教训你！
EN: Even the police car dared to attack. See how I give you a lecture

CN: 像你这种弱不禁风的，我一个打十个！
EN: I can fight ten men by myself！
Meat bomb chariot!Charge!

CN: 死亡冲撞！看我不把你给你撞飞！
EN: Death collision! Now, I'm going to hit you

CN: 看到我出现就代表你已经死了！
EN: When you see me, it means you are dead!

CN: 让你见识见识重量的厉害！
EN: Let you see how powerful the weight is!

CN: 欢迎来到管不了街区，虽然这里现在几乎是一片废墟，但是在高明的投资人的眼里这里就是一块儿赚钱的宝地。
EN: Welcome to the block, although it is now almost a ruins, but in the eyes of clever investors here is a place to make money.

CN: 我是交易所为你派来的助手，愿意花100美元投资这里的人肯定是个天才，所以交易所派我来全力帮助你。
EN: I am the assistant that the exchange sent for you. The person who is willing to spend $100 to invest here must be a genius, so the exchange sent me to help you.

CN: 签上这份合同，你就是这里新的管理人了
EN: You'll be the new manager here when you sign this contract.

CN: 这就是你发财的地方了，但首先你需要恢复社区的一些基础建筑设施
EN: This is where you make a fortune, but first you need to restore some infrastructure in the community.

CN: 废话不多说，现在这儿就是基本就是一片废墟，先修建一个建筑试试吧
EN: Cut the crap!Now here is almost in ruins. Try to build a structure first.

CN: 恭喜你建好了第一个建筑，离成功已经不远了
EN: Congratulations on the completion of your first building, you are not far from success.

CN: 每个建筑都能给你带来一些好处，你现在已经是街区负责人了，收一些保护费也是应该的。
EN: You are now the person in charge of the block, and every building here can bring you some benefits, so you could charge some protection fees.

CN: 即便你离开了，保护费也会不停累计，不用担心会收不到
EN: Even if you leave, the protection fee will continue to accumulate, so you don’t have to worry about not receiving it.

CN: 街区经常会有一些烟草商开车来卖一些货品，等他们的黑市车到街区时，就可以使用烟草买一些稀有货品了。
EN: There are often some tobacco merchants who drive to the block to sell some goods, and when they get to the block, you can use tobacco to buy some rare goods.

CN: 好了，现在来试试投币吧，投币是最主要获得奖励的方式，多多投币获得奖励发展你的社区吧！
EN: Well, now let's try to coin.The most primary way to get rewards is to coin. Now let's get rewards by coining more coins to develop your community!

CN: 你现在已经完全掌握了所有技巧了，好好利用这些金币发展你的街区吧

EN: There are the cars of the bosses in the block. These bosses are very stingy. The gold coins will be sucked in as soon as they touch bosses's car.

CN: 看见车上那个头像了吗？吸得太多这些大佬会亲自出来抢你的金币，击败他们可以得到丰厚的奖励噢！
EN: Did you see the profile picture in the car? If you suck too many gold coins, these boss will personally come out to grab your gold coins. Defeating them can get rich rewards!

CN: 街区大佬来了！我先溜了。你加油，别被大佬把你钱抢跑了。

EN: But if you beat the block boss, you can get a lot of rewards. Best of luck.

CN: 恭喜你街区发展已经恢复了正常，为了奖励你的勤奋，私人再免费送你一个作弊技能。
EN: Congratulations! The development of the block has returned to normal. In order to reward your diligence, I will give you a cheating skill for free.

CN: 这个技能能让你选择一个你想用的技能装备上，就能在得到皇冠币或美元币时，免费试用这个技能了。

CN: 什么？你问为什么不能直接免费使用，大哥，天下怎么可能有免费的午餐？
EN: What? You ask why you can't use it directly for free? Hey guys, there's no such thing as a free lunch!

CN: 夜总会的灯亮了，把金币从灯的中间穿过，就有机会获得大奖，不赶快试试吗？
EN: The lights come on in the nightclub. If you pass coins through the middle of the lamp, you have a chance to win a big prize. Why don't you try it out?

CN: 恭喜你解锁了财富金猪，掉落到废水池里的美元会被金猪捡起来，在累计到上限之前砸开金猪就可以获得被被金猪捡起的美元，不用再担心美元被冲走了。
EN: Congratulations on unlocking the Fortune Golden Pig. Dollars that fall into the wastewater pools will be picked up by the golden pig. Before the cumulative amount reaches the upper limit, you can get the dollars picked up by the golden pig by breaking the golden pig. You no longer have to worry about the dollar being washed away.

CN: 在你不在的时候，一伙其他社区的帮派成员偷袭了我们社区，抢了我们一大笔钱走！
EN: When you were away, a group of gang members in other communities attacked our community and took us a lot of money away!

CN: 不管怎样，先把建筑修好，没提前告诉你做好防御准备是我的错，这次就帮你免费修理，下一次修理可就要收费了。
EN: Anyway,you fix the building first. It is my fault that didn't tell you in advance that you need to be prepared for defense. This time I will help you repair it for free, but the next repair will be charged.

CN: 虽然建筑是修好了，但是这口气可咽不下去，这次免费教你，让你知道我们这行的规矩该怎么做！

CN: 好了，现在就去让这些家伙见识见识咱们的手段！

CN: 抢夺破坏其他社区可以得到一笔奖金，好好利用这笔奖金吧。

EN: You can get points after pushing down the coins, and the accumulated points can improve your level.

CN: 提升段位可以获得很多不错的奖励，并且随着段位提升，还能提升自己的游戏排名。
EN: You can get a lot of good rewards when you level up, and as you level up, you can also improve your game ranking.

CN: 段位可在排行榜内查看，多多提升自己的实力吧
EN: The level can be checked in the leaderboard, more to improve your own strength.

CN: 看来每个社区管理人都很努力了，祝你早日成为第一黑帮第一社区。
EN: It seems that every community manager has worked very hard, and I wish you will become the first community in the first Mafia as soon aspossible.

CN: 恭喜你解锁了第二个作弊技能
EN: Congratulations on unlocking the second cheating skill.

CN: 赶快厚着脸皮试试这个第二个技能吧
EN: let's try quickly the second skill!

EN: The former block bosses knew about you, and now their cars appear on your block.

CN: 居然中了美元大奖，这些绿色的币就是你累计财富的方式，获得这些币可以直接获得美元，美元可以用来建设你的街区。
EN: You hit the dollar jackpot.These green coins are the way you accumulate wealth. These green coins can be directly exchanged for U.S. dollars, which can be used to build your block.

CN: 绿色的币可以通过启动老虎机，礼物箱，以及大佬们赠送等方式落入奖池，好好努力获得更多的美元吧。
EN: Green coins can be obtained not only by launching slot machines and gift boxes, but also by gifting by boss. Work hard to get more dollars.

CN: 社区里会有一些小贩通过面包车的方式卖一些平常买不到的东西，只要你有足够的美元，就能够买到一些好东西。
EN: There will be vendors in the community selling something through vans that is not normally available and will be able to get some good stuff as long as you have enough dollars.

CN: 快去黑市看看吧，点击左下方黑市贩卖车试试
EN: Let's go to the illegal market! Try to click on the bottom left illegal market'car.

CN: 好好利用街道赚的钱，买一些需要的道具吧。
EN: Make good use of the money earned on the street to buy some necessary props.

CN: 恭喜你把币推入了红色的框，老虎机启动了，运气好的话有机会获得大奖
EN: Congratulations on pushing the coins into the red box, so the slot machine has started, and if you are lucky, you have a chance to win a prize.

CN: 击败头领会有很丰富的奖励，当然头领也不是轻易能击败的，灵活运用旁边的技能能更快的击败头领。
EN: If you defeat the leader, you will win a rich reward. Of course, the leader is not easy to defeat, you can use nearby skills to defeat the leader faster.

CN: 使用火力全开技能可以提高子弹的攻击力
EN: Using full-firing skills can improve the attack power of the bullet.

CN: 使用急速射击技能，可以提高子弹发射的速度。
EN: The use of rapid shooting skills can increase the speed of bullet launching.

CN: 可以通过点击转动炮台，更容易攻击到头领。
EN: It is easier to attack the leader by clicking to turn the turret.

CN: 你已经掌握了战斗技巧了，快击败头领获得奖励吧
EN: You have mastered the combat skills, go to defeat the boss and get rewards.

CN: 恭喜你获得了一个道具，每个道具第一次获得都可以在道具展示中获得奖励
EN: Congratulations on obtaining an item, each item can be rewarded in the item display when you get it in the first time.

CN: 刚刚等级提升解锁了新的作弊技能，赶快去街道试试吧
EN: New cheating abilities have been unlocked after levelling up, so go to the streets and try them out.

CN: 这抖动可真夸张，不同的技能可以为你带来不同的收益，尽量使用技能获得奖励吧
EN: What a dramatic shake! Different skills can bring you different rewards, so try to use them to get rewards.

CN: 在发展社区的过程中，也有一些社区的任务需要你完成，当然不会让你白干，完成之后会获得一些奖励。
EN: In the process of developing the community, there are also some community tasks that you need to complete, which of course will not let you do it in vain. You will get some rewards after completion.

CN: 看来你已经完成了第一个社区任务，快点击领取你的奖励吧。
EN: It seems that you have completed your first community mission. Click to receive your reward.

CN: 社区任务还可以通过快捷方式查看和进入，点击上方快捷按钮即可进入查看社区任务
EN: Community tasks can also be viewed and entered through shortcuts. Click the shortcut button above to enter and view community tasks.

CN: 当敌人出现时，炮台可以用来攻击敌人，但是初期炮台的威力有限，可以通过升级炮台来提高炮台威力。
EN: When the enemy appears, batteries can be used to attack them, but their power is limited at first, and can be improved by upgrading them.

CN: 你的选择很多，首先选择需要升级炮台
EN: You have a lot of choices, first of all you need to upgrade the battery.

CN: 目前其他炮台还未解锁，只能升级已有的炮台，当其他炮台解锁后，即可进行升级并使用，点击“升级”对炮台进行升级。
EN: At present, other batteries are not unlocked, only existing batteries can be upgraded. When other batteries are unlocked, they can be upgraded and used. Click "Upgrade" to upgrade the battery.

CN: 炮台已经准备就绪，只要再派遣人员即可进行升级
EN: The battery is ready and can be upgraded by sending more personnel.

CN: 通过推币奖励获得的人偶，可用于人员派遣。炮台升级途中所需要的材料，同样可通过推币的道具奖励获得。
EN: The dolls obtained through coin push rewards can be used for personnel dispatch. The materials needed to upgrade the batteries can also be obtained through the prop rewards of pushing coins.

CN: 升级炮台不仅可以提升威力，同时可以获得更强力的技能效果，努力升级炮台应对更强力的敌人吧
EN: Upgrading batteries not only increases power, but also gives you more powerful skills. Striving to upgrade batteries to deal with more powerful enemies.

CN: 派遣人偶后，炮台会进行升级，并且大幅缩短升级时间，通过上方的进度条可以查看升级的进度
EN: After the dolls are dispatched, the turret will be upgraded, and the upgrade time can be greatly shortened. You can check the progress of the upgrade through the progress bar above.

CN: 恭喜你将社区恢复了活力，现在可以将你的社区进行大规模升级了
EN: Congratulations on revitalizing your community and now you can upgrade your community on a massive scale.

CN: 在完成建筑升级后，可以再次升级社区，努力将你的社区打造成顶级社区吧。
EN: After you've completed your building upgrade, you can upgrade your community again and try to make your community a top-notch community.
